OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough Council is stepping up
OL,7,Fefforts to reclaim more than #67
OL,8,Fmillion in unpaid debts.
OL,10,FOf the overall figure, more than half
OL,11,F(#36.8 million) is uncollected council
OL,12,Ftax, up by #2.1 million in the past
OL,13,Ftwelve months.
OL,15,FOther sources of unpaid debt include
OL,16,F#8.4 million in business rates and
OL,17,F#15.5 million in uncollected sums for
OL,18,Fpaid-for council services.
