OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,FThe council says it will take a "firm
OL,7,Fbut fair" approach but will launch
OL,8,Flegal action to recover debts where
OL,9,Fnecessary.
OL,11,FA council report says council tax and
OL,12,Fbusiness rates are a key funding
OL,13,Fsource for the local authority,
OL,14,Faccounting for around 66 per cent of
OL,15,Fits income.
