OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,F"Through a comprehensive collection
OL,7,Fstrategy, underpinned by the council's
OL,8,FWelfare Strategy for both business and
OL,9,Fresidents, the council will pursue
OL,10,Fdebt in a firm but fair way," the
OL,11,Freport says.
OL,13,F"Residents and businesses will be
OL,14,Foffered a range of support to resolve
OL,15,Fdebt problems, such as maximising
OL,16,Fbenefit, welfare advice and support,
OL,17,Fdebt management, crisis support all of
OL,18,Fwhich form part of the support on
OL,19,Foffer.
