OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,F"Where payment is not forthcoming the
OL,7,Fcouncil will exercise its powers
OL,8,Fprovided under the relevant
OL,9,Flegislation to enforce the debt.
OL,11,F"Some of these powers are significant
OL,12,Fand can lead to serious consequences
OL,13,Fsuch as attachment to earnings,
OL,14,Fremoval of goods,forcing the sale of a
OL,15,Fproperty or even commitment to prison
OL,16,Fall of which are powers enshrined in
OL,17,Flaw."
