OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,FHowever, the report also warns that
OL,7,Ffollowing a rise in council tax of
OL,8,F4.99 per cent - the maximum rise
OL,9,Fpermitted - collecting debts will
OL,10,Fcontinue to be a challenge, due to
OL,11,Fhigh levels of deprivation, benefit
OL,12,Fcaseloads and low levels of income.
OL,14,FThe process of collecting ageing
OL,15,Fbusiness rates was also described as
OL,16,F"problematic" in the report, with the
OL,17,Fcouncil left with few recovery options
OL,18,Fin cases where businesses have ceased
OL,19,Ftrading or filed for bankruptcy.
