OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,FAcross the country, council tax
OL,7,Farrears have hit a record high of #6
OL,8,Fbillion and National Debtline reports
OL,9,Fthat a third of callers to its service
OL,10,Fhad council tax arrears in May, making
OL,11,Fit the most common priority debt.
OL,13,FOn average, National Debtline callers
OL,14,Fowe on average #1,762 in arrears ` an
OL,15,Fincrease of 49 per cent from #1,181 in
OL,16,F2019.
