OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,FSteve Vaid, chief executive of the
OL,7,FMoney Advice Trust, the charity which
OL,8,Fruns National Debtline, said: "Council
OL,9,Ftax debt is on a worrying upward trend
OL,10,Fand the sheer scale of arrears now
OL,11,Funderlines the need for urgent action.
OL,12,FBut this is nothing new.
OL,14,F"Council tax continues to be one of
OL,15,Fthe most common debts amongst our
OL,16,FNational Debtline clients, and recent
OL,17,Fcost of living pressures have left
OL,18,Fmany more people struggling to keep up
OL,19,Fwith their payments.
