OL,3,CMiddlesbrough Council aims to recover
OL,4,Cmore than #67 million in unpaid debts
OL,6,F"Councils have a vital role in helping
OL,7,Fresidents with unmanageable bills and
OL,8,Fto ensure council tax, crucial to
OL,9,Ffunding local services, is collected
OL,10,Fin a way that is fair and affordable.
OL,12,F"Reforming collection practices should
OL,13,Fbe a priority for the next government,
OL,14,Fincluding putting an end to people
OL,15,Fbecoming liable for their full annual
OL,16,Fcouncil tax bill after falling behind."
